OL,6,FA parent carer group which represents
OL,7,Faround 1000 families in says
OL,8,Fcouncillors who made 'discriminatory'
OL,9,Fcomments about children with Special
OL,10,FEducational Needs and Disabilities ()
OL,11,Fand their parents should resign.
