OL,3,CAnger as councillor says some children
OL,4,Cwith SEND are 'just badly behaved'
OL,6,FCllr Jeff Morgan, Cllr Brian
OL,7,FHammersley and Cllr Clare Golby have
OL,8,Fbeen criticised for the language they
OL,9,Fused in the meeting held at
OL,10,FWarwickshire Council on 25 January.
OL,12,FCllr Morgan, the former cabinet member
OL,13,Ffor children and young people queried
OL,14,Fwhether some SEND children 'were just
OL,15,Freally badly behaved' and 'needed a
OL,16,Fform of strict correction'.
OL,18,FCllr Hammersley asked: "Was there
OL,19,Fsomething in the water?" and "Where
OL,20,Fwere they all when I was at school?"
