OL,6,F"I think it's important that they (the
OL,7,Fcouncillors) acknowledge that they are
OL,8,Faware and understand why their
OL,9,Flanguage was harmful and that they
OL,10,Facknowledge that in their apology.
OL,11,FThey need to actually acknowledge why
OL,12,Fthey need to apologise. And in this
OL,13,Fcase, it was the use of discriminatory
OL,14,Flanguage.
