OL,3,CAnger as councillor says some children
OL,4,Cwith SEND are 'just badly behaved'
OL,6,F"I was extremely alarmed that nobody
OL,7,Fin that chamber batted an eyelid when
OL,8,Fthe comments were made which told me
OL,9,Fhow common that type of conversation
OL,10,Fis. It worries me that it's become
OL,11,Fhabitual and there is a culture that
OL,12,Fthat type of attitude is acceptable.
OL,13,FAnd so for that reason, I don't think
OL,14,Fthat those councillors should be
OL,15,Fholding a seat of office."
