OL,6,FLast night Cllr Jeff Morgan wrote in
OL,7,Fhis statement: "As a former Cabinet
OL,8,Fmember and councillor of nine years I
OL,9,Fregret any offence caused by my choice
OL,10,Fof words. It was never my intention to
OL,11,Foffend and I regret the words I used
OL,12,Fto make a point about demand and need
OL,13,Fin the SEND area. I remain committed
OL,14,Fto the children and families of
OL,15,FWarwickshire."
