OL,6,FCouncillor Brian Hammersley said: "I
OL,7,Fapologise unreservedly for the
OL,8,Fcomments which I made at the recent
OL,9,FScrutiny Committee. I regret my
OL,10,Fclumsiness and lack of care in
OL,11,Fchoosing my words and can see the
OL,12,Fupset and offence caused. I am
OL,13,Fterribly sorry and will be more
OL,14,Fthoughtful with my questions and words
OL,15,Fin the future. I can see that I have
OL,16,Fsome learning to do."
