OL,3,CAnger as councillor says some children
OL,4,Cwith SEND are 'just badly behaved'
OL,6,FCouncillor Izzi Seccombe, the leader
OL,7,Fof Warwickshire County Council, said
OL,8,Fin a statement today that she wanted
OL,9,Fto offer reassurance that those views
OL,10,Fand language used were not
OL,11,Frepresentative of the council, its
OL,12,Fwider councillors and staff or their
OL,13,Fcommitment to children and young
OL,14,Fpeople especially those with SEND.
OL,16,FThe Chief Executive of the council
OL,17,FMonica Fogarty emphasised that the
OL,18,Fmatter was being taken extremely
OL,19,Fseriously and that time now needed to
OL,20,Fbe allowed for an investigation to be
OL,21,Fcompleted.
